Dire Straits & Mark Knopfler - Private Investigations (The Best Of) (2005) [FLAC] {2 CD}

Released 	2005
Genre 		Rock
Label 		Mercury

Private Investigations: The Best of Dire Straits 
and Mark Knopfler is a 2005 best of album. It is 
composed of material by Dire Straits and the solo 
career of the lead guitarist and singer, Mark Knopfler. 
The US version omits "Darling Pretty" but adds "Skateaway.
